data.description:
***Back on the market at NO fault to the seller!!! Brand new roof just installed***

Don’t miss an opportunity to own your dream home in the coveted Four Pillars neighborhood in the award winning Grain Valley school district! This beauty is an expansive 4 bedroom, 3 bedroom reverse ranch with extras throughout. From the formal dining room to the sitting room off the kitchen, the main level laundry to the spacious basement storage, it really has it all! The kitchen is perfect for cooking and entertaining with the granite countertops and updated appliances. Plus the gathering space transitions easily onto the composite deck out back with a full outdoor living space! The primary en suite boasts two separate vanities, a spacious shower and jetted bathtub as well as a large walk-in closet. In the basement, there is another full living room that walks out to an additional outdoor living space on the back patio. This home backs up to the community walking trail making it the perfect setup to enjoy living in such a peaceful setting in a great location just minutes from I-70 and all of the Adam’s Dairy shopping and amenities.
